          Contest winners will selected by the Contest judges based on the judging criteria and rules of the Contest. The decision of the judges shall be final. One (1) prize will be reserved for the 'People's Choice' award, which will awarded to the Entry with the most votes on the Contest website. SCB-TO will not communicate with participants about the results of the photo contest.
        %li 
